title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E04 Journey with Fear
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea 
S04E04 
Journey with Fear

First aired: October 15, 1967

Crane and Morton are transported to Venus by aliens from the planet Centaur, who want to stop humans from exploring the galaxy. 

Nelson: Richard Basehart Crane: David Hedison. Morton: Bob Dowdell. Centaur I: Gene Dynarski. Centaur II: Jim Gosa. Wilson: Eric Matthews
